{"id":"lyr_5qKF6Imz6Iqz_MjkwOQ_0016","text":"倦了麼亂了麼 多得你帶引我起過","structure":{"line_index":16,"char_count":14},"semantics":{"themes":["支持","鼓勵","成長"],"sentiment":"VERY_POSITIVE","keywords":["倦","亂","帶引","起過"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,5,3,2,5,3,3,3,5,4,5,5,9,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["gyun6","liu5","mo1","lyun6","liu5","mo1","do1","dak1","nei5","daai3","jan5","ngo5","hei2","gwo3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"倦","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"了","pos":"PART"},{"text":"麼","pos":"PART"},{"text":"亂","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"了","pos":"PART"},{"text":"麼","pos":"PART"},{"text":"多得","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"帶引","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我起","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"過","pos":"PART"}],"syntax_notes":"再次使用「倦了麼」、「亂了麼」，但這次是感謝對方的「帶引」，使自己重新振作。"},"source":{"title":"歌之女","artists":["梅豔芳"],"lyricists":["林振強"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2909","prev_line_id":"lyr_5qKF6Imz6Iqz_MjkwOQ_0015","next_line_id":"lyr_5qKF6Imz6Iqz_MjkwOQ_0017","paragraph_id":"para_05"}}
{"id":"lyr_5qKF6Imz6Iqz_MjkwOQ_0017","text":"若永可爲你歌 便再不需得到什麼","structure":{"line_index":17,"char_count":14},"semantics":{"themes":["滿足","愛","追求"],"sentiment":"VERY_POSITIVE","keywords":["為你歌","得到","什麼"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,5,9,5,3,2,4,3,3,3,4,2,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["joek6","wing5","ho2","nei5","go1","bin6","zoi3","bat1","seoi1","dak1","dou3","sam6","mo1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"若永可爲","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"歌","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"便","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"再","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"不","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"需","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"得到","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"什麼","pos":"PRON"}],"syntax_notes":"「若永可為你歌」是條件句，表達只要能為對方唱歌，便不再追求其他事物，顯示了極大的滿足感。"},"source":{"title":"歌之女","artists":["梅豔芳"],"lyricists":["林振強"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2909","prev_line_id":"lyr_5qKF6Imz6Iqz_MjkwOQ_0016","next_line_id":"lyr_5qKF6Imz6Iqz_MjkwOQ_0018","paragraph_id":"para_05"}}
{"id":"lyr_5qKF6Imz6Iqz_MjkwOQ_0018","text":"凝望你找到愛找到我","structure":{"line_index":18,"char_count":9},"semantics":{"themes":["愛","連結","自我"],"sentiment":"VERY_POSITIVE","keywords":["凝望","找到","愛","我"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,2,5,9,4,4,9,4,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jing4","mong6","nei5","zaau2","dou3","oi3","zaau2","dou3","ngo5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"凝望","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"找到","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"愛","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"找到","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"}],"syntax_notes":"「凝望你找到愛找到我」簡潔有力，表達了在對方身上找到了愛與自我。"},"source":{"title":"歌之女","artists":["梅豔芳"],"lyricists":["林振強"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2909","prev_line_id":"lyr_5qKF6Imz6Iqz_MjkwOQ_0017","next_line_id":"lyr_5qKF6Imz6Iqz_MjkwOQ_0019","paragraph_id":"para_05"}}
{"id":"lyr_5qKF6Imz6Iqz_MjkwOQ_0019","text":"我記起當天的一個小歌女 她聲音不太嬌","structure":{"line_index":19,"char_count":17},"semantics":{"themes":["回憶","歌女","聲音"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["記起","歌女","聲音","嬌"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,4,9,3,3,3,4,9,3,5,3,3,3,3,4,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ngo5","gei3","hei2","tin1","dik1","jat1","go3","siu2","go1","neoi5","taa1","sing1","jam1","bat1","taai3","giu1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"記起","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"當天","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"一個","pos":"DET"},{"text":"小","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"歌女","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"她","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"聲音","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"不太嬌","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"再次以「我記起」開頭，這次描述歌女的聲音特質，與「不太嬌」形成對比。"},"source":{"title":"歌之女","artists":["梅豔芳"],"lyricists":["林振強"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2909","prev_line_id":"lyr_5qKF6Imz6Iqz_MjkwOQ_0018","next_line_id":"lyr_5qKF6Imz6Iqz_MjkwOQ_0020","paragraph_id":"para_06"}}
{"id":"lyr_5qKF6Imz6Iqz_MjkwOQ_0020","text":"唱出隱隱滄桑她唱出空虛 但眼睛始終閃也耀","structure":{"line_index":20,"char_count":19},"semantics":{"themes":["情感","歌女","堅韌"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["滄桑","空虛","眼睛","閃耀"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[4,3,9,9,3,3,3,4,3,3,3,2,5,3,9,3,9,5,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["coeng3","ceot1","jan2","jan2","cong1","song1","taa1","coeng3","ceot1","hung1","heoi1","daan6","ngaan5","zing1","ci2","zung1","sim2","jaa5","jiu6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"唱","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"出","pos":"PART"},{"text":"隱隱","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"滄桑","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"她","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"唱","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"出","pos":"PART"},{"text":"空虛","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"但","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"眼睛","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"始終","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"閃","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"也","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"耀","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「唱出隱隱滄桑」、「唱出空虛」描繪了歌女的內心感受，但「眼睛始終閃也耀」則展現了她的生命力。"},"source":{"title":"歌之女","artists":["梅豔芳"],"lyricists":["林振強"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2909","prev_line_id":"lyr_5qKF6Imz6Iqz_MjkwOQ_0019","next_line_id":"lyr_5qKF6Imz6Iqz_MjkwOQ_0021","paragraph_id":"para_06"}}
{"id":"lyr_5qKF6Imz6Iqz_MjkwOQ_0021","text":"或有天她都可叫座 她也許有天不再餓","structure":{"line_index":21,"char_count":16},"semantics":{"themes":["希望","歌女","未來"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["叫座","不再餓"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,5,3,3,3,9,4,2,3,5,9,5,3,3,4,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["waak6","jau5","tin1","taa1","dou1","ho2","giu3","zo6","taa1","jaa5","heoi2","jau5","tin1","bat1","zoi3","ngo6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"或","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"有","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"天","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"她","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"都","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"可","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"叫座","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"她","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"也許","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"有天","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"不再","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"餓","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"重複第11行的歌詞，再次強調對歌女未來成功的期盼。"},"source":{"title":"歌之女","artists":["梅豔芳"],"lyricists":["林振強"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2909","prev_line_id":"lyr_5qKF6Imz6Iqz_MjkwOQ_0020","next_line_id":"lyr_5qKF6Imz6Iqz_MjkwOQ_0022","paragraph_id":"para_06"}}
{"id":"lyr_5qKF6Imz6Iqz_MjkwOQ_0022","text":"夏與秋與歌飄過 過了不知已過","structure":{"line_index":22,"char_count":13},"semantics":{"themes":["時光","流逝","回憶"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["夏","秋","歌","飄過","已過"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,5,3,5,3,3,4,4,5,3,3,5,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["haa6","jyu5","cau1","jyu5","go1","piu1","gwo3","gwo3","liu5","bat1","zi1","ji5","gwo3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"夏","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"與","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"秋","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"與","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"歌","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"飄過","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"過","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"了","pos":"PART"},{"text":"不知","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"已過","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「夏與秋與歌飄過，過了不知已過」以季節的更迭比喻時光的流逝，帶有淡淡的感慨。"},"source":{"title":"歌之女","artists":["梅豔芳"],"lyricists":["林振強"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2909","prev_line_id":"lyr_5qKF6Imz6Iqz_MjkwOQ_0021","next_line_id":null,"paragraph_id":"para_06"}}
